This paper involves the evaluation and design of neural architectures for a specific task suite involving mathematics problems in a free-form textual input/output format. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE), and Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV).
